Listen above to Part 1 THE FORUM, the ideas programme with BRIDGET KENDALL. Indian Nobel laureate and economist, AMARTYA SEN on fighting injustice. Swedish crime writer HENNING MANKELL on imagination as a tool for survival. British Iranian psychotherapist CAMILA BATMANGHELIDJH on creating a soothing repertoire for children. Show less